    public class SecuredSeqImpl
extends SecuredContainerImpl
implements SecuredSeq
    Implementation of SecuredSeq to be used by a SecuredItemInvoker proxy. Sequence may have breaks in the order. http://www.w3.org/TR/2004/REC-rdf-mt-20040210/#Containers
